CHANGES IN VERSION 0.8
----------------------

  o plotBitScatter(x, y = NULL) now also works for x being a two-column matrix

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.7
----------------------

  o add functions to calculate and plot phasograms, e.g. to measure nucleosome
    repeat length in MNase data (R/phasograms.R, src/phasograms.cpp)

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.6
----------------------

  o added tests for sampleControlElements() to cover all code (coverage gaps detected with covr::zero_coverage(covr::package_coverage()))

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.5
----------------------

  o sampleControlElements() now catches cases with too few control elements to match the target distribution

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.4
----------------------

  o sampleControlElements(x = list(), ...) now works correctly

